Leah Ray https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leah_Ray 0 Leah Ray Hubbard Werblin (February 16, 1915 – May 27, 1999) was an American singer and actress born in Norfolk, Virginia who performed in the Big Band era and who sang and acted in more than a dozen motion pictures.
